  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Shadow King has invaded the castle belonging to the Knights of Valor and they need your help to get it back! Explore the massive castle in this metroidvania and help the fallen knights back to their former glory! Upgrade your moves and weapons along the way as you fight minions, defeat bosses, find secrets, and unravel what has happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/8a3835c206cfae0cc81f58f7477198d6.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interconnected map with graphically unique areas!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quirky cast of different enemies! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun platforming all around!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights and secret rooms!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful and engaging soundtrack!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/8e8365546ca77d642a82779c02a05608.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=42 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREDITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Code, pixel art, and design: Johan Peitz</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music and SFX: José Ramón \"Bibiki\" García</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capsule Art: Jon Nielsen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/4eb6419676b7182c50f2562f4af6114f.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=36 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Shadow King has invaded the castle belonging to the Knights of Valor and they need your help to get it back! Explore the massive castle in this metroidvania and help the fallen knights back to their former glory! Upgrade your moves and weapons along the way as you fight minions, defeat bosses, find secrets, and unravel what has happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/8a3835c206cfae0cc81f58f7477198d6.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interconnected map with graphically unique areas!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quirky cast of different enemies! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun platforming all around!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights and secret rooms!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful and engaging soundtrack!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/8e8365546ca77d642a82779c02a05608.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=42 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREDITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Code, pixel art, and design: Johan Peitz</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music and SFX: José Ramón \"Bibiki\" García</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capsule Art: Jon Nielsen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2675390/extras/4eb6419676b7182c50f2562f4af6114f.webp?t=1748894853\" width=300 height=36 /></span></p>",
